<h1>How do I use this?</h1>
<p><font size="4"><b>1)</b> Put in the person's username in the username text box. <br><br>

<b>2)</b> Put their MAC address in the next textbox - <br>
(WITH THE CORRECT FORMAT xx:xx:xx:xx:xx:xx or xx-xx-xx-xx-xx-xx)!!! <br><br>

<b>3)</b> Put the device type where it says "Device type" e.g 'Playstation' 4 or 'Roku Tv' (no quotes) <br><br>

<b>4)</b> Then finally, put your first and last name in the last textbox <br><br>

After that everything should be done and they should be set to connect to the network!
</font></p>